## 🧬 Memory System

| Memory Type | Storage | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Short-Term | Redis (`REDIS_URL`) | Current session state, agent scratchpads |
| Long-Term / Episodic | Chroma Cloud | Vector store of past research findings + metadata (topics, timestamps), reusable across sessions |

> **Assumption:** dropped the separate PostgreSQL long-term store from the earlier version since it's not in your `.env` — long-term context now lives as metadata alongside vectors in Chroma Cloud. Say the word if you'd rather add Postgres back for structured user/session data.

