## 🛠️ Tools Agents Can Use (all free/no paid API keys)

- **Web Search:** `duckduckgo-search` (DuckDuckGo, free, no API key, no rate-limit charges) + `scholarly` for Google Scholar
- **Scraping:** Playwright (free, open source) with stealth mode for JS-heavy sites
- **Academic:** Semantic Scholar API + arXiv API (both free, no key required)
- **PDFs:** PyMuPDF + Unstructured.io (open-source/free tier) for parsing
- **Embeddings:** Local `sentence-transformers` models (e.g. `all-MiniLM-L6-v2`) — no API calls, runs on CPU
- **Code Execution:** Sandboxed local Python for data analysis, if needed

