## 📊 Observability & Evaluation

- **Tracing:** Structured local logging (JSON lines per agent call) or self-hosted [Langfuse](https://langfuse.com) (open-source, free to self-host) instead of LangSmith
- **Custom metrics** tracked per agent: call count, latency, token usage
- **RAGAS** metrics: faithfulness, answer relevancy, context precision — using Groq (with Gemini fallback) as the judge LLM
- **Custom metrics:** citation accuracy, source diversity, hallucination rate
- **Resource controls:** per-query call/token counters to keep Groq/Gemini free-tier usage within rate limits

---

## 🛡️ Guardrails

- PII scrubbing before sending content to the LLM
- Prompt injection detection on scraped/search content
- Max 3 reflection iterations to prevent infinite loops

